column1: Bilateral Remittance Estimates for 2012 using Migrant Stocks, Host Country Incomes, and Origin Country Incomes (millions of US$) (May 2013 Version)

These estimates are based on the methodology developed by Ratha and Shaw, 2007, "South-South Migration and Remittances," Development Prospects Group, World Bank (www.worldbank.org/prospects/migrationandremittances).  The remittance data is for 2012, disaggregated using host country and origin country incomes from 2011, and estimated migrant stocks from 2010.

*The unidentified category refers to countries for which there are data on total remittance inflows, but where estimates of bilateral migrant stocks are unavailable to enable disaggregation by remittance source country.
